        "title": "Installation of Tube Wells and Water Purification Plants",
        "description": "With your support, we ensure access to clean drinking water for the needy. Join us in this humanitarian effort.",
        "content": "<h3>Program Details</h3><p class='editor-paragraph editor-empty'></p><div data-youtube-video=\"\"><iframe class=\"editor-youtube-video\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" autoplay=\"false\" disablekbcontrols=\"false\" enableiframeapi=\"false\" endtime=\"0\" ivloadpolicy=\"0\" loop=\"false\" modestbranding=\"true\" origin=\"\" playlist=\"\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-Lc6SqHCMsI\" start=\"0\"></iframe></div><p class=\"editor-paragraph editor-empty\"></p><p class='editor-paragraph'>Many regions of Bangladesh still suffer from a severe shortage of safe and drinkable water. Particularly in areas affected by drought, salinity, and arsenic contamination, people endure extreme hardship to meet their daily water needs. As a result, they often suffer from waterborne diseases, face serious health risks, and experience a significantly diminished quality of life. To address this crisis, As-Sunnah Foundation has initiated the installation of tube wells and construction of water purification plants in remote and underserved regions, aiming to ensure access to clean water so that people in these areas can lead healthier, more dignified, and improved lives.</p>",
